{"tid":470563,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦用用下會無左畫面，想重新開機都熄唔到機","createTime":"2017-11-16T11:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T10:38:00.000Z","uid":126327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da254be13e0d2f459d433a3ad5bbf99ff41c7db7","tid":470563,"uid":126327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"電腦白痴 想問下各位巴打<br />\n前排砌左部新電腦 用左幾日出左事<br />\n有時用用下個mon會無啦啦 no signal<br />\n但我望部主機 樣樣野都run緊<br />\n底板 顯示卡 水冷 機箱風扇 都郁緊<br />\n之後我諗住restart部機啦<br />\n點知禁機箱個制無反應<br />\n長禁左幾分鐘 都唔熄機 <br />\n禁restart制都restart唔到<br />\n最後要啪機箱後面粒電源制先可以熄到<br />\n之後再開返又無事<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況試過幾次<br />\n仲有試過幾次boot機開唔到os<br />\n唔知巴打們知唔知我部腦有咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSpec:<br />\nCPU: AMD - Ryzen 7 1700 3.0GHz 8-Core Processor<br />\nCPU cooler: Corsair - H100i v2 70.7 CFM Liquid CPU Cooler<br />\nGraphic card: Asus - PRIME X370-PRO ATX AM4 Motherboard<br />\nRam: Corsair - Vengeance LED 16GB (2 x 8GB) DDR4-3000 Memory<br />\nSSD: Samsung - 960 EVO 250GB M.2-2280 Solid State Drive<br />\nGraphic card: Gigabyte - GeForce GTX 1070 8GB G1 Gaming Video Card<br />\nPower supply: GX750 - CM Storm Edition<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b7f2654387ed23f865c8e8331d910921fbcc26","tid":470563,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"火牛出事機率大<br />\n火牛750W都係得80 PLUS Bronze<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe2648d42576f1464ff0f9e854b645675db299e","tid":470563,"uid":126327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火牛出事機率大<br />\n火牛750W都係得80 PLUS Bronze<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問下80plus bronze意思係咩？<br />\n唔夠力推？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.g